pull the codeblocks out of a markdown file. returns a string.

usage:
  import tangle from "*tangle*"
  import fs from "node:fs/promises"
  let doc = await fs.readFile("readme.md")
  let code = tangle(doc)

also provides a cli.

usage:
  node tools/tangle/index.js readme.md

the name was knuth's idea.
